name: Rizen Coin
public_notice:
Rizen has recently undergone a chain migration to BSC network. More information at https://coinrizen.medium.com/introducing-rizencoin-into-binance-smart-chain-f8b99d6f5279
Old Rizen token page may still be traded but is no longer official supported by the team
additional_notices: Kindly be aware that liquidity provided in Automated Market Maker platforms (eg. Uniswap, Sushiswap, Balancer) can be removed (also known as rug pulling), resulting in a collapse of available liquidity. Please exercise caution when trading! This notice is NOT directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder for our users.

description.en:
Rizencoin is the native token of the Rizen ecosystem, and a community centric project on BSC combining proof of stake, proof of liquidity and proof of transaction. Rizen as the first experimental community-driven DeFi project with unique staking and supply mechanism. Rizen gives you lifetime passive reward from staking which can anytime and instantly be withdrawn. The more transactions happen the more reward you will get from staking.

Rizen supply is reduced by burning 1% fee from unstaking, and the 1% fee (from withdrawal of staking rewards, buy/sell, and transfers) is instantly distributed to stakers.
